text: WTQT-LP (106.1 FM) is a low-power FM (LPFM) radio station offering gospel music. The station began on May 8, 2003, and is licensed to Baton Rouge, Louisiana. It broadcasts with an ERP of 71 watts and is available on the Internet. ==External links== * Category:Radio stations in Louisiana Category:Low-power FM radio stations in Louisiana Category:Gospel radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2003
